                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/6995" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">CSR-0157</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">7831 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">“期货+保险”：国元证券为猪贴上“护身符”</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">“Futures + Insurance”: Guoyuan Securities Puts a “Amulet” on Pigs</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">魏玖长，王晨曦</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中国科学技术大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">王晨曦</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">国元证券股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">贸易与金融业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">12 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">金融扶贫；金融服务创新；“保险+期货”；风险管理</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"> Financial poverty alleviation; Financial service innovation; “Insurance + Futures”; Risk management</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">近年来，生猪价格剧烈波动和饲料价格持续走高，严重阻碍广大养殖户持续稳定盈利。农牧产品价格波动风险是许多贫困县域农业发展面临的共同问题。当前，我国正处于精准扶贫关键时期，乡村振兴战略稳步推进阶段。缺少风险规避的渠道与工具一直是制约农业产业发展壮大和脱贫攻坚任务的重点。本案例以国元期货桦南县猪饲料成本价格指数“保险+期货”项目助力桦南县脱贫攻坚为主线，描述了国元证券作为一家国有金融机构，通过利用自身专业优势，为农户提供金融工具防范风险，大大提高了生猪产业的“容错率”，解除了养殖场企业的后顾之忧。本案例重点阐述了金融机构如何通过模式创新提高金融服务能力，为贫困地区赋能，以及“保险+期货”助农、惠农模式的原理，对“三农”和贫困地区开展金融服务，推进精准扶贫工作提供借鉴与参考。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">In recent years, the price of pigs fluctuated drastically and the price of feed continued to rise, which seriously hindered the farmers&#39; stable profits. The risk of price fluctuation of agricultural and animal husbandry products is a common problem faced by many poor counties. At present, China&#39;s targeted poverty alleviation has entered a critical period, and the strategy of Rural Revitalization is in the initial stage. But the lack of channels and tools to avoid risks has always been the focus of restricting the development of agricultural industry and the task of getting rid of poverty. In this case, the &quot;Insurance + Futures&quot;, Pig Feed Cost Price Index in HuaNan County, of Guoyuan Futures, which takes helping this county get rid of poverty as the main line, this paper describes that Guoyuan Securities, as a state-owned financial institution, provides farmers with financial instruments to prevent risks by taking advantage of its professional advantages, which greatly improves the &quot;fault tolerance rate&quot; of pig industry and relieves the worries of farm enterprises. This case focuses on how financial institutions improve their ability on financial service through model innovation,  empowering poor areas. It highlights the principle of how the &quot;insurance plus futures&quot; model benefits agriculture, providing reference to solve &quot;the issue of agriculture, farmer and rural areas&quot;, as well to carry out financial services and promote targeted poverty alleviation in developing areas.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2020</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《商业伦理》、《风险管理》、《金融市场学》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">金融扶贫；金融服务创新；企业社会责任；“保险+期货”；涉农金融产品；风险分担机制</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023-01</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">查看全文:</th>
